               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350105-name-196" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350105-name-196" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350105-name-196" type="surname" value="TOPLIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350105-name-196" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD TOPLIS</persName>
                  </hi>. On Sunday afternoon, the 21st of December, about five minutes after three o'clock, I was going to church—just by Shoreditch church gate I missed my handkerchief out of my pocket—I did not feel it taken—I made a stand for a moment, and a witness called out, "I have got him," and in a minute the prisoner was brought up to me with it in his possession.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
